    "href": "mailto:capsulecatgames@gmail.com"
  }, "capsulecatgames@gmail.com"), " or by post to:"), mdx("p", null, "Capsule Cat\n7520 S 13th Pl\nPhoenix, AZ 85042\nUnited States"), mdx("h2", null, "HOW CAN YOU REVIEW, UPDATE, OR DELETE THE DATA WE COLLECT FROM YOU?"), mdx("p", null, "Based on the laws of some countries, you may have the right to request access to the personal information we collect from you, change that information, or delete it in some circumstances. To request to review, update, or delete your personal information, please visit: ", mdx("a", {
